channel.title: The Conway & Clohessy Tree
channel.description: A family tree of the ancestors and relatives of Thomas Conway [b1900 - d1980] and Bridie Clohessy [b1904 - d1986]

item.title: Added Noonan, Foley and Fitzgerald families
item.description: Originally I left out part of the tree because I had found a discrepancy between the information I had received on the Cusacks and the records (avilable online) for some of those people. I chose to leave that part of the tree out until I had a better understanding, because it wasn't clear where the diffeences were coming from. I can now add the relevant people to the tree. Thanks to Jerry Russell and Hugh Sweeney for the information.
